title: Wrigleyville 2 bedroom - In Unit Laundry - Central A/C
posting_body: ['Wrigleyville 2 bedroom - In Unit Laundry - Central A/C - Gut Renovated!', '817 W Addison - 817-GR, Chicago, IL, 60613', '$2095 per month', 'Available September 1st', '2 beds, 1 full bath', '850 sq.', 'ft.', 'Condo quality, rehabbed apartment with in unit laundry, central air, hardwood floors, granite counter tops, upgraded stainless steel appliances, and dishwasher!', 'Spacious living room with bright, modern lighting.', 'Both bedrooms will comfortably fit a queen size bed.', 'Lots of closet and cabinet space.', 'Kitchen has pantry!', 'Your own private outdoor space.', 'Beautiful tile and vanity in the newly renovated bathroom.', 'In the heart of Lakeview, steps to the lake, shopping, public transportation options, restaurants, Whole Foods, Jewel, Wrigley Field, Red Line Train Station, just about one block away!', 'A 96 neighborhood walk score!', 'Central a/c and heat make this an amazing choice in the middle of it all!', 'Dogs and cats okay.', ' Paid parking garage across the street!', 'Rooms and Interior', '.', 'Recently rehabbed', '.', 'Condo quality', '.', 'Hardwood floors', '.', 'Living room', '.', 'Garden apartment', '.', 'Ceiling fans', 'Kitchen and Bath', '.', 'Kitchen recently updated', '.', 'Granite kitchen counters', '.', 'Hardwood cabinets', '.', 'Stainless steel appliances', '.', 'Dishwasher', '.', 'Refrigerator', '.', 'Stove / oven', '.', 'Microwave', '.', 'Modern bath fixtures', 'Utilities and Extras', '.', 'Central heat', '.', 'Central air conditioning', '.', 'Laundry in unit', 'Building and Surroundings', '.', 'Gated property', 'Lease Terms', '.', 'Dogs ok', '.', 'Cats ok', 'Contact Us:', '312.725.6847']
